<p>
<em>Most of the sections below are currently empty.</em>

<sect>X server
<p>
Unlike the 3.3.x versions, there is now a single X server binary (called
<tt>XFree86</tt>.  This binary can either have one or more video drivers
linked in statically, or, more usually, dynamically load the video drivers
and other modules that are needed.

<em>more intro details here</em>

